001package org.biopax.paxtools.impl.level3;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.model.BioPAXElement;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.DeltaG;
005
006import static java.lang.Float.compare;
007
008
009public class DeltaGImpl extends ChemicalConstantImpl implements DeltaG {
010
011    private float deltaGPrime0 = UNKNOWN_FLOAT;
012
013
014    public DeltaGImpl() {
015    }
016
017    //
018    // BioPAXElement interface implementation
019    //
020    ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
021    public Class<? extends DeltaG> getModelInterface() {
022        return DeltaG.class;
023    }
024
025
026    protected boolean semanticallyEquivalent(BioPAXElement element) {
027        return super.semanticallyEquivalent(element) && (compare(((DeltaG) element).getDeltaGPrime0(), deltaGPrime0) == 0);
028    }
029
030
031    public int equivalenceCode() {
032        return super.equivalenceCode()+
033                29 + deltaGPrime0 != +0.0f ?
034                Float.floatToIntBits(deltaGPrime0) : 0;
035    }
036
037    public float getDeltaGPrime0() {
038        return deltaGPrime0;
039    }
040
041    public void setDeltaGPrime0(float deltaGPrime0) {
042        this.deltaGPrime0 = deltaGPrime0;
043    }
044
045}
